(47, '4th Annual FirestormÂ® Charity Golf Tournament', 0, 0, 'Firestorm Event', '1500530400', '1:00pm', '', '9:00pm', 0, 'Legacy Ridge Golf Course', '10801 Legacy Ridge Parkway', '', 'Westminster', 'CO', '80031', 1, 'thirdparty', 'https://www.eventbrite.com/e/4th-annual-firestorm-charity-golf-tournament-tickets-33817220216', 50, '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666a73; font-family: ''Benton Sans'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Get ready for THE Firestorm&reg; event of the summer! Our 4th Annual Firestorm&reg; Charity Golf Tournament is going to be epic! First off, let''s talk about who we are supporting this year!</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: #666a73; font-family: ''Benton Sans'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span style="font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px;"><img style="border: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; padding-top: 0px;" src="https://cdn.evbuc.com/eventlogos/2674146/zw4mlogocropped.jpeg" alt="Zach''s Wishes For Miracles" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: #666a73; font-family: ''Benton Sans'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: #666a73; font-family: ''Benton Sans'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Zach&rsquo;s Wishes for Miracles provides uplifting experiences to young adults ages 18 &ndash; 23, fighting for their lives. We wholly believe these experiences can, and do, make life better for both the young adult and their family at a time when it matters most. In order to maximize our impact, we operate with an entirely volunteer staff. As a 501(c)(3) your donations not only go directly to the experiences, but they are also 100% tax deductible. Learn more at&nbsp;<a style="color: #0278b8; text-decoration-line: none; padding-top: 0px;" href="http://www.zw4m.org/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">www.Zw4m.org</a></p>\r\n<h2 class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: #282c35; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-family: ''Benton Sans'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Now, on to tournament details!</h2>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: #666a73; font-family: ''Benton Sans'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">This is going to be a scramble tournament, meaning that each player will tee off and play will continue from the spot of the BEST shot from the foursome. This makes it fun, fast and friendly for all ability levels! We will have a shotgun start at 1:30pm. Play should take roughly 5 - 5 1/2 hours and we will be serving dinner immediately following the tournament. There will be an awards ceremony, live entertainment as well as a silent auction. Please register your foursome ASAP as this tournament will sell out quickly!</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: #666a73; font-family: ''Benton Sans'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Additionally, for interested companies, we are offering some sponsorships. All of the sponsorship dollars go to the charity. We run lean and mean with no fluff! And since ZW4M is a 501(c)3 your sponsorships could be tax deductible (please consult your tax professionals). Here are the levels.</p>\r\n<h2 class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: #282c35; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-family: ''Benton Sans'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span style="padding-top: 0px;">Platinum Sponsor - $25,000 (1 Available)</span></h2>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: #666a73; font-family: ''Benton Sans'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">As a Platinum Sponsor for the 4th Annual Firestorm&reg; Charity Golf Tournament, benefitting Zach&rsquo;s Wishes for Miracles, your firm is assured HIGH visibility before, during and after the tournament. Sponsorship includes:</p>\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px 2em; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #666a73; font-family: ''Benton Sans'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Corporate name/logo incorporated as Platinum Sponsor into all promotional emails, social media posts, marketing materials, and event pages leading up to the tournament.</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px;">A dedicated email post event to our attendees</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px;">A press release naming and thanking our sponsors</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px;">Corporate name/logo on all printed materials at tournament</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px;">Full page acknowledgement on back cover of event program</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px;">Corporate name/logo recognition on event banner PLUS one separate banner prominently displayed at tournament</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px;">Opportunity to display promotional materials and/or provide additions to our swag bags</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px;">Corporate name/logo recognition on our event pages and website</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px;">